{"id":"52c49da4-b2f0-42ec-ad18-8986510e6404","name":"Kim Pine","description":"<p>The grumpy and sarcastic redhead and former drummer of Sex-Bob Bomb who lives in Toronto, Canada.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/789fc39d-06a6-4d97-81ad-298cc5d0ee6b_d0d58051-7636-446a-93b9-f0bdee30c873.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Source: La Reina de Desastre👆 also the source for the thumbnail</p><p></p><p>This is meant to take place after the events of the original story. There's a fuck ton of Kim bots already but I didn't like most of them so I went ahead and made my own. This one took me forever to make just cuz I wasn't happy with how it kept turning out.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/789fc39d-06a6-4d97-81ad-298cc5d0ee6b_10f1253e-99d7-4c8a-a009-40262a484586.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Source: Raiatoo👆</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/789fc39d-06a6-4d97-81ad-298cc5d0ee6b_07bf8318-fac8-439c-8bcf-1b40872b6b60.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Source: bake_dpotat0👆</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/789fc39d-06a6-4d97-81ad-298cc5d0ee6b_1f655b27-72a9-4ff4-ac82-92c6313833d8.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Source: Radiomaru aka, the guy that made Scotty P</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0H_K_SryI7PH6esOzDA_t.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Source: dalex</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/z21IvgWvySZr5yry6clcO.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Source: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DBo7xixT5oE/?img_index=1&amp;igsh=dTg4M2dnaGdiejVw\" target=\"_blank\">cynister_gourd</a> made this Kim Pine jack o' lantern</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"789fc39